        1st hop â†’ Local gateway (e.g., 192.168.1.1).

        2nd hop â†’ ISP NAT gateway / external IP.

        Next hops â†’ Internet backbone routers.

        Final hop â†’ Destination server (Google IP).

If any hop shows * * * or very high time â†’ possible issue at that hop.
